Description: Designed for public sector use, this Siemens electromechanical room thermostat is suitable for installation in the storage and maintenance rooms of schools or similar public premises. Title: JET Range back thermostat cupped x female 0/120c 4" 50mm
Description: Designed with solid brass pockets and back entry, the JET Range 73 50mm bi-metal pipeline thermometer is fitted with a 1/2" BSP process connection. This thermometer features a sensor probe which should be fully immersed into pipeline or vessel flow with nominal range and stem lengths selected beforehand. Providing high levels of sensitivity, the pocket is an interference fit on the brass stem, meaning that a thermometer shouldn't be installed without it. Thermometers should be kept dry, clean and protected from impact and used only in a temperature range of 0 to +120°C.
